high_descs: go to the counter to the left of the stove
pick up the lettuce from the counter
take the lettuce to the fridge
put in the fridge then remove
take the chilled lettuce back to the counter
put the lettuce back on the counter
anns.task_desc: chill the lettuce then return it to the counter

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the fridge, then turn right and walk to the counter on the left side of the stove.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the counter.
Walk left back to the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge, to the left and behind the tan plate. Close the door, wait a moment, and take it out again.
Take a couple steps right, facing the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the head of lettuce on the plate on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled head of lettuce on a plate on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right, go across the room, turn right and go to the dishwasher.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn left and go to the dishwasher.
Put the lettuce on the counter in front of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a head of chilled lettuce on the counter.
